月光？没有啊？
Moon? I can't see it

653
00:36:57,833 --> 00:37:00,417
那么大的月亮你没看到吗？看清楚点
There is a big moon. Can you see it?

654
00:37:00,708 --> 00:37:02,792
天还没有黑，那来的月光
It's not dark yet, how come is there a moon?

655
