玉皇大帝眼见如此
heaven Emperor saw that

682
00:38:08,167 --> 00:38:10,333
因此给孙悟空一个机会转世
He gave the monkey a chance to revive

683
00:38:10,542 --> 00:38:12,417
安排他们师徒今世在这里重逢
He planned the master and the disciple to meet here

684
00:38:12,667 --> 00:38:14,792
继续去完成取西经的使命
Then they can finish the journey to the west

685
